object.customQuery:
SELECT distinct quoteinfo.UniqueId, quoteinfo.SystemId, quoteinfo.CMMContainer, quoteinfo.ApplicationNumber, quoteinfo.CustomerRef, quoteinfo.CustomerNumber, quoteinfo.Status, quoteinfo.TypeCd, quoteinfo.AddDt, quoteinfo.AddTm, quoteinfo.AddUser, quoteinfo.UpdateDt, quoteinfo.UpdateTm, quoteinfo.UpdateUser, quoteinfo.SubmittedDt, quoteinfo.FirstMailedDt, quoteinfo.LastMailedDt, quoteinfo.CloseReasonCd, quoteinfo.CloseSubReasonCd, quoteinfo.CloseSubReasonLabel, quoteinfo.CloseDt, quoteinfo.CloseTm, quoteinfo.CloseUser, quoteinfo.CloseComment, quoteinfo.Branch, quoteinfo.BusinessSourceCd, quoteinfo.CarrierCd, quoteinfo.CarrierGroupCd, quoteinfo.ChangeDt, quoteinfo.Comments, quoteinfo.CompanyProductCd, quoteinfo.ControllingStateCd, quoteinfo.EffectiveDt, quoteinfo.ExpirationDt, quoteinfo.FinalPremiumAmt, quoteinfo.FullTermAmt, quoteinfo.ExpiringPremiumAmt, quoteinfo.WrittenPremiumAmt, quoteinfo.InceptionDt, quoteinfo.PayPlanCd, quoteinfo.PolicyDisplayNumber, quoteinfo.PolicyRef, quoteinfo.PreviousCarrierCd, quoteinfo.PreviousExpirationDt, quoteinfo.PreviousPolicyNumber, quoteinfo.PreviousPremium, quoteinfo.ProductVersionIdRef, quoteinfo.ProviderRef, quoteinfo.ProviderCd, quoteinfo.SubProducerCd, quoteinfo.SubTypeCd, quoteinfo.TransactionCd, quoteinfo.TransactionCommissionAmt, quoteinfo.UnderwriterCd, quoteinfo.FullTermFeeAmt, quoteinfo.FinalFeeAmt, quoteinfo.ExpiringFeeAmt, quoteinfo.WrittenFeeAmt, quoteinfo.CommercialName, quoteinfo.PrimaryPhoneName, quoteinfo.PrimaryPhoneNumber, quoteinfo.SecondaryPhoneName, quoteinfo.SecondaryPhoneNumber, quoteinfo.FaxNumber, quoteinfo.EmailAddr, quoteinfo.MailingAddr1, quoteinfo.MailingAddr2, quoteinfo.MailingAddr3, quoteinfo.MailingAddr4, quoteinfo.MailingCity, quoteinfo.MailingStateProvCd, quoteinfo.MailingPostalCode, quoteinfo.MailingLatitude, quoteinfo.MailingLongitude, quoteinfo.MailingCounty, quoteinfo.MailingCountyCode, quoteinfo.MailingRegionCd, quoteinfo.MailingRegionISOCd 
FROM
 quoteinfo where quoteinfo.CMMContainer='Application' and quoteinfo.SystemId in (select SystemId from advrxxchangedbeans where CMMContainer='Application' AND 
concat(adddt,addtm)>='2022-11-09 00:00:00.000' and concat(adddt,addtm) <='2024-03-09 00:00:00.000' )
